venice.lib.networkRSB

Class RSBHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • rsb.AbstractEventHandler
      • venice.lib.networkRSB.RSBHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, rsb.Handler

    public class RSBHandler
extends rsb.AbstractEventHandler
    Waits for new RSB-Events and transfers the received RSB-data to the master-listener (of the application that uses this library).

    This handler is normally added to every RSB in-slot by the RSBNamespaceBuilder.

    It will also take care of class-matching, if present.
